title: Ep 2027 - Funny Performances
shortDesc: Babita and Komal organize a funny contest where two random members of Gokuldham society are paired up and are asked to perform a task.

title: Ep 2028 - Champaklal Ka Classical Dance
shortDesc: Bagha and Bawri entertain the members of Gokuldham society with their dance act. Daya challenges Champaklal to show his classical dance skills.

title: Ep 2029 - Kathputli Dance
shortDesc: Madhavi and Daya perform kathputli dance on the occasion of Ganesha festival. Iyer challenges Taarak and Anjali to perform a poetry in front of all members of Gokuldham society.

title: Ep 2030 - Champaklal Punishes Iyer and Jethalal
shortDesc: Iyer and Jethalal stop dancing while performing an act. Champaklal punishes the duo to clean up the hall.

title: Ep 2031 - Taarak Ki Kavita
shortDesc: Taarak and his neighbors gather to drink soda. Taarak informs them that a poet is going to meet him next day.

title: Ep 2032 - Kavi Sammelan
shortDesc: Mr. and Mrs. Sharma come to Taarak Mehta’s house. Daya asks Jethalal to go to Taarak’s house at the earliest. Taarak Mehta and his neighbors gather for poetry conference.

title: Ep 2033 - Sharma Ki Kavitaye
shortDesc: Mr. and Mrs. Sharma share innovative poetries with the members of Gokuldham Society. Mr. Sharma tells Jethalal and his friends that the wives can never keep secrets.

title: Ep 2034 - Mr. Sharma Ka Challenge
shortDesc: Mr. Sharma asks Jethalal and his neighbors to tell their wives one secret and see whether they will tell it to anyone or not. Jethalal asks Bagha to bring CCTV cameras to Gokuldham Society.

title: Ep 2035 - Dr. Hathi Ka Top Secret
shortDesc: Dr. Hathi and his friends decide to tell their random secrets to their wives and to check whether they will tell it to anyone or not. Dr. Hathi tells a secret of Bhide to his wife. He instructs her to not reveal the secret to anyone.

title: Ep 2036 - Patni Pariksha
shortDesc:
Bhide asks Bagha to install CCTV cameras in the club house. Jethalal reminds his wife to not reveal Mehta’s secret to her friends.

title: Ep 2037 - Mission Patni Pariksha
shortDesc: Daya and her neighbors gather in the clubhouse for meeting. They start revealing the secrets of each others’ husbands. On the other hand, Jethalal and his friends watch the live telecast of the meeting on a television.

title: Ep 2038 - Jethalal and Friends in Club House
shortDesc: Jethalal and his friends enter the club house. They angrily ask their wives as to why they revealed their secrets to each other. They also inform the wives that they were watching their discussion through CCTV camera.

title: Ep 2039 - Navratri Ki Tayyari
shortDesc: Daya tells Jethalal that she is going to club house to teach ‘garba’ to her friends. Bavri requests Bagha to buy passes for ‘garba’ program.

title: Ep 2040 - Gokuldham Society Gears Up For Garba Celebrations
shortDesc: Madhavi and her friends teach garba to their husbands. Popatlal tells his neighbours that they may not be able to arrange garba function in Gokuldham Society.

title: Ep 2041 - Garba Festival Ki Tayyari
shortDesc: All-in-one bhai decides to threaten Bhide to not organize Garba festival in Gokuldham society. Later, he comes to Jethalal’s shop and orders speakers for his mega Garba celebration.
